file.name: resourceowner-component.openapi.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Resource Owner Component
  description: Component
  version: 1.0.0

paths: {}

components:
  schemas:
    MultipleResourceOwner:
      type: object
      required:
        - total
        - resource_owners
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        resource_owners:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResourceOwner'
    ResourceOwner:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - profile
        - type
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        group_id:
          type: string
        user_id:
          type: string
        author_id:
          type: string
        profile:
          type: object
          properties:
            display_name:
              type: string
            website:
              type: string
        type:
          type: string
